show.description: David’s rebel heart skips a beat when he fakes a love story to dodge an arranged marriage, only to stumble into a real one. But what happens when a fake girlfriend says no to the drama? Tune in for a bold romantic rollercoaster packed with sharp twists and unexpected sparks. Watch Now.
